    <abstract>
      <para>
<application>&App;</application> provides a way for blind individuals to access
scanned sheet music in a convenient format (&bmn;).
      </para>
      <para>
This book serves as an introduction to &bmn; for those readers that are not
familiar with it yet.  It is also the User's Manual for
<application>&App;</application>.
      </para>
    </abstract>
  </bookinfo>

  <part><title>Introduction to &bmn;</title>
    <partintro>
      <para>
&bmn; is an internationally accepted standard for expressing musical ideas in
tactile readable form.
      </para>
      <para>
Since <application>&App;</application> is mostly useless to a user who does not
know &bmn;, the first part of this book is dedicated to teaching the very
basics of &bmn;.  If you are already familiar with the international &bmn;
standard, you can saves skip over this section.
      </para>
    </partintro>

